precis:
Amendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS Schedule No. 756 restricting
sale to certain sizes, pharmaceutical forms and strengths of
chloramphenicol and requiring a warning statement on the labelling of
chloramphenicol products which would explicitly prohibit their use in
food-producing animals.
